name: Student Monthly Attendance Sheet-range
query:
SELECT
  `tabStudent Attendance`.register_number as "Register Number:Readonly:120",  
  `tabStudent Attendance`.student_name as "Student Name:Readonly:200",
   COUNT(`tabStudent Attendance`.status) as "CS6551 (Days Present):select:150"
FROM
  `tabStudent Attendance`
WHERE
  (`tabStudent Attendance`.date BETWEEN '2018-07-28' AND '2018-08-25') and
  `tabStudent Attendance`.student_group = 'CS6551/B.Tech in Information Technology/A/2018-19 (Sem5)' and
  `tabStudent Attendance`.status ='Present'
   group by `tabStudent Attendance`.student_name
   order by `tabStudent Attendance`.register_number asc
